{"tid":2130141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"李顯龍的侄仔李繩武，因為係Facebook出post嘲笑新加坡法治而被罰款15000坡元","createTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:45:44.000Z","uid":48040,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eb276864cb0712163fd181ce2e92c01a23ac34d1","tid":2130141,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:10:19.000Z","msg":"新加坡高等法院今天（29日）宣判，總理李顯龍的侄子李繩武藐視法庭罪成，須罰款1萬5000新元（約32萬元台幣）或坐牢一周。旅居美國多年的李繩武則在臉書表示「不同意」判決結果，擔憂執政的人民行動黨此後會變本加厲打壓人民政治言論。<br />\n<br />\n路透報導，2017年，李顯龍與弟弟李顯揚、妹妹李瑋玲因父親李光耀故居拆建問題起糾紛，一度鬧上法院。李顯揚長子李繩武在長輩們決定私下解決後，於臉書撰文指「新加坡政府非常好爭訟，又有順從的司法制度」，質疑新加坡司法制度的獨立性。今年稍早，檢方正式以藐視法庭罪起訴李繩武。<br />\n <br />\n新加坡《聯合早報》報導，法官今天宣判時指出，李繩武的臉書貼文「無疑是在批評我國司法制度，而且按照常理，他應預料到這樣的貼文會被人轉載和引起媒體報導的興趣」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200729/QS23SOICXDJGD54BTNZHYAX2CQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200729%2FQS23SOICXDJGD54BTNZHYAX2CQ%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6XqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=13c3f4e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200729%2FQS23SOICXDJGD54BTNZHYAX2CQ%2F&h=5ff5cf3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200729/QS23SOICXDJGD54BTNZHYAX2CQ/</a>"},{"pid":"71532c7463aff61f65506a4528d45563260ab5ca","tid":2130141,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:11:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf3475ab423aa0643be20e71b59e6599f4a2f46e","tid":2130141,"uid":54502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"人在美國，鐘意講咩都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb52fa1f2ef4cece56153f6e0aa4d9f31606decb","tid":2130141,"uid":268153,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"Monkey 仔以為自己國家好自由<img src=\"/assets/fac